{"tid":1643772,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[推到連仔見到]求吓大家幫吓我朋友 佢唔想出名啊","createTime":"2019-10-10T09:39:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T08:34:36.000Z","uid":153615,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"505602af961626a691fc1602692ad259e249db30","tid":1643772,"uid":153615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T09:39:57.000Z","msg":"是咁的，今日起身見到有條片傳緊，發現係我同學，所以就tg搵佢問佢安唔安全，下面就係我同佢嘅對話<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EVKVqTw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEVKVqTw.png&h=050caf3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原來佢上咗呢個post<br />\n<br />\n[突發] 教材級示範 中學生淡定應對黑警恐嚇盤查 EQ震驚全港市民<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1642421\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1642421</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n明白大家都好欣賞佢呢種行為想教吓其他手足學佢咁冷靜面對黑警，但係條片入面有佢嘅個人資料，所以希望大家為咗手足嘅安全同私隱幫手叫連仔del咗個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個post唔係我開所以唔知開喺站務台有冇用<br />\n<br />\n唔知有咩可以證明到我係佢同學，各位巴絲唔信嘅話可以搵啲嘢叫我證明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但首先求吓大家幫我推咗個post先，手足安全要緊啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75f34f379f3612ba61191cc5ed7f525a5f1b8049","tid":1643772,"uid":153615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T09:40:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"301cc2a214517096972087be8f558f0531145f4c","tid":1643772,"uid":153615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T09:40:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4a9a6f3fcd56a20333c9e73bd67f122c5e1486a8","tid":1643772,"uid":153615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T09:41:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5fd54fcfbff3178fad138ccf376bcb4012b30d17","tid":1643772,"uid":153615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T09:43:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"06b7960da9d4043eea892ca857712af07f6f4cd1","tid":1643772,"uid":153615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score